snippet.title: India's Fourfold Attack On Pakistan After Uri Attacks

localized.description:
India is mulling on the MFA status given to Pakistan and campaigning is being done to declare Pakistan as a terror state in US. More than 1,19,000 people have signed a petition submitted to the White House to declare Pakistan as a terror state.
